<!DOCTYPE html>


<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Slide 25 - Cierre</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .slide-container {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .text-corporate-blue {
            color: #114a90;
        }
        .bg-corporate-blue {
            background-color: #114a90;
        }
        .text-corporate-red {
            color: #C0504D;
        }
        .bg-corporate-red {
            background-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-red {
            border-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-blue {
            border-color: #114a90;
        }

        .profile-image-container {
            position: relative;
        }
        .profile-image-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -10px;
            left: -10px;
            right: 10px;
            bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #C0504D;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .profile-image-container::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            right: -10px;
            bottom: -10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #114a90;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .social-icon-link {
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
        }
        .social-icon-link:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .qa-bubble {
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slide-container font-poppins">
<header class="w-full h-24 flex items-end justify-between px-12 pb-4 relative z-10">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-corporate-red"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
<span class="w-8 h-1 bg-corporate-red"></span>
<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Conclusión</p>
</div>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-corporate-blue">Fin del Taller</h2>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-end">
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">25</p>
</div>
</header>
<main class="flex-1 px-12 py-6 flex flex-col justify-center items-center relative z-10">
<div class="w-full max-w-4xl flex flex-col items-center gap-10 mt-12">
<div class="text-center">
<h1 class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-corporate-blue mb-4">¡Gracias!</h1>
<div class="w-24 h-2 bg-corporate-red mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-light">
                    Espero que estas herramientas te ayuden a transformar tu presencia digital.
                </p>
</div>
<div class="w-full grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mt-4">
<div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center relative overflow-hidden group hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-corporate-blue"></div>
<div class="profile-image-container w-32 h-32 mb-6 relative z-10">
<div class="w-full h-full rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-4 border-white shadow-sm relative z-10">
<img alt="Lolo Avatar" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://www.genspark.ai/api/files/s/g2LOdxVh"/>
</div>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">Lolo</h3>
<p class="text-corporate-red font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">Estratega Digital</p>
<div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-3">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-corporate-blue flex items-center justify-center">
<i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i>
</div>
<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium">info@lienzolabs.com</p>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-corporate-blue flex items-center justify-center">
<i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin-in"></i>
</div>
<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium truncate w-full text-left">Lolo González-Mohino</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center relative">
<div class="qa-bubble w-24 h-24 bg-corporate-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-5xl shadow-lg mb-6 relative z-10 border-4 border-white">
<i class="fa-solid fa-question"></i>
</div>
<div class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-4 h-4 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full qa-bubble" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>
<div class="absolute top-4 right-10 w-6 h-6 bg-corporate-blue rounded-full qa-bubble" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">¿Tienes dudas?</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        Aprovecha este momento para resolver cualquier inquietud sobre la estrategia, las herramientas o la implementación.
                    </p>
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 bg-corporate-blue text-white rounded-full font-semibold shadow-md cursor-pointer hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors">
<i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i>
<span>Abrimos Turno de Preguntas</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute -left-20 top-40 w-64 h-64 bg-gray-50 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-70 -z-10"></div>
<div class="absolute -right-20 bottom-20 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-50 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-70 -z-10"></div>
</main>
</div>

    <div style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-family: sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <a href="/slide-25" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Anterior</a>
        <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">26 / 26</span>
        <a href="#" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 0.5; pointer-events: none">Siguiente</a>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>

